  "title": "All-Party Parliamentary Group on Antimicrobial Resistance",
  "purpose": "The APPG exist to raise the profile of antimicrobial resistance, the need to preserve antimicrobials (including antibiotics, antivirals, antifungals, and antiparasitics) through education on their appropriate uses (including non-human uses), the lack of new treatments for infections and to help accelerate efforts to discover, research and develop new treatments.",
